query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(kt t) NoHashJoin(kt miidx t it) NoMergeJoin(it kt miidx t mi) NoMergeJoin(it kt mi miidx t mc) NoNestLoop(it kt mc mi miidx t ct) NoHashJoin(ct it kt mc mi miidx t cn) NoMergeJoin(cn ct it kt mc mi miidx t it2) */ select min(cn.name) AS producing_company,
min(miidx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS movie_about_winning
from kind_type AS kt
inner join title AS t
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'episode' AND t.title <> '' AND ( t.title like '%Champion%' OR t.title like '%Loser%')
inner join movie_info_idx AS miidx
on miidx.movie_id = t.id
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = miidx.info_type_id AND it.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = t.id AND mi.movie_id = miidx.movie_id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = t.id AND miidx.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'distributors'
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[de]'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'release dates';
